                </svg>
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="project-showcase">
          <div class="project-image-container">
            <img src="/images/project-addition1.jpg" alt="Home addition with large windows and modern design" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="project-details">
            <h3>Modern Home Addition</h3>
            <p class="project-location">Maple Grove</p>
            <p>700 sq. ft. addition featuring a family room with vaulted ceilings and a home office space.</p>
            <div class="project-meta">
              <span>Duration: 12 weeks</span>
              <span class="project-rating">
